#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:1
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Configuratie"

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:4
msgid ""
"Configure Resthome — rooms and sectors, INAMI rates and packages, supplement"
" types, health insurers, facility and multi-company."
msgstr ""
"Resthome configureren — kamers en sectoren, tarieven en RIZIV-forfaits, "
"supplementtypes, mutualiteiten, instelling en multi-vennootschap."

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:7
msgid ""
"Before day-to-day use, a few basic settings give Resthome its structure. "
"They are set up once, then only change at the margins."
msgstr ""
"Vóór het dagelijkse gebruik structureren enkele basisinstellingen Resthome. "
"Ze gebeuren één keer en evolueren daarna nog nauwelijks."

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:9
msgid "Application settings"
msgstr "De instellingen van de applicatie (Settings)"

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:11
msgid ""
"The **Settings** menu brings together all the parameters, organized by tab. "
"For a nursing home (MR/MRS), follow these guides — each one details **every "
"field** and its **recommended value**:"
msgstr ""
"Het menu **Instellingen** bundelt alle parameters, per tabblad. Voor een "
"woonzorgcentrum (WZC/RVT) volgt u deze gidsen — elk beschrijft **elk veld** "
"en de **aanbevolen waarde**:"

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:13
msgid "[General settings (residents, rooms)](reglages-generaux.md)"
msgstr "[Algemene instellingen (bewoners, kamers)](reglages-generaux.md)"

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:14
msgid "[Billing settings (MR/MRS)](reglages-facturation.md)"
msgstr "[Facturatie-instellingen (WZC/RVT)](reglages-facturation.md)"

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:15
msgid "[eHealth and eFact settings](reglages-ehealth.md)"
msgstr "[eHealth- en eFact-instellingen](reglages-ehealth.md)"

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:16
msgid "[Meals and nutrition settings](reglages-repas.md)"
msgstr "[Instellingen voor maaltijden en voeding](reglages-repas.md)"

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:17
msgid "[Document settings](reglages-documents.md)"
msgstr "[Documentinstellingen](reglages-documents.md)"

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:19
msgid "Rooms and sectors"
msgstr "Kamers en sectoren"

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:21
msgid ""
"**Rooms**: create your rooms, with their **type** (MR, MRS, single or double"
" room…) and their **amenities**."
msgstr ""
"**Kamers**: maak uw kamers aan, met hun **type** (ROB, RVT, één- of "
"tweepersoonskamer…) en hun **uitrusting**."

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:22
msgid "**Sectors / units**: group rooms by living unit."
msgstr "**Sectoren / eenheden**: groepeer de kamers per leefeenheid."

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:23
msgid ""
"A room can be set to **maintenance**, **reserved**, or switched back to "
"**automatic** assignment based on occupancy."
msgstr ""
"Een kamer kan in **onderhoud** of **gereserveerd** gezet worden, of terug op"
" **automatische** toewijzing volgens de bezetting."

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:25
msgid "Rates and packages"
msgstr "Tarieven en forfaits"

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:27
msgid ""
"**INAMI rates**: the **package** amounts per **Katz category** — the basis "
"for health-insurer reimbursement."
msgstr ""
"**RIZIV-tarieven**: de bedragen van het **forfait** per **Katz-categorie** —"
" de basis van de mutualiteitsterugbetaling."

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:28
msgid "**Accommodation rates**: the room price (resident's share)."
msgstr "**Verblijfstarieven**: de prijs van de kamer (bewonersaandeel)."

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:29
msgid ""
"**Supplement types**: the catalog of billable services (see "
"[Supplements](../facturation/supplements.md))."
msgstr ""
"**Supplementtypes**: de catalogus van factureerbare prestaties (zie [De "
"supplementen](../facturation/supplements.md))."

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:30
msgid ""
"**Absence discount rules** and **AViQ codes**: the fine-tuning of billing."
msgstr ""
"**Regels voor afwezigheidskorting** en **AVIQ-codes**: de fijne "
"parametrering van de facturatie."

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:32
msgid "Health insurers and reference data"
msgstr "Mutualiteiten en referentiegegevens"

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:34
msgid ""
"**Health insurers (insurance organizations)**: the list used for "
"insurability and eFact."
msgstr ""
"**Mutualiteiten (verzekeringsinstellingen)**: de lijst gebruikt voor de "
"verzekerbaarheid en de eFact."

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:35
msgid ""
"**Facility**: your home's information (identifiers, contact details) used in"
" documents and eHealth submissions."
msgstr ""
"**Instelling**: de gegevens van uw huis (identificatienummers, "
"contactgegevens) gebruikt in de documenten en de eHealth-verzendingen."

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:37
msgid "Multi-company"
msgstr "Multi-vennootschap"

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:39
msgid ""
"Resthome handles **multiple companies** in a single database: each company "
"has its own residents, rooms and billing, kept separate. Useful for a group "
"that operates several facilities."
msgstr ""
"Resthome beheert **meerdere vennootschappen** in eenzelfde database: elke "
"vennootschap heeft haar bewoners, haar kamers en haar facturatie, "
"afgeschermd. Nuttig voor een groep die meerdere instellingen uitbaat."

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:41
msgid "The activity log"
msgstr "Het activiteitenlogboek"

#: ../../content/configuration/index.md:44
msgid ""
"An **activity log** tracks access to sensitive data (GDPR). It can be viewed"
" from the configuration — useful for compliance."
msgstr ""
"Een **activiteitenlogboek** traceert de toegangen tot gevoelige gegevens "
"(GDPR). Het is raadpleegbaar vanuit de configuratie — nuttig voor de "
"compliance."

